room_title: Escape room "The Shipwreck" by Sherlock's Escape Rooms in Florence (KY)
room_description: An old pirate shipwreck has washed ashore along the coast of a small Caribbean island. Within it live many secrets and hidden treasures, including the missing coins in the precious treasure chest. You have only one hour to find the coins and escape the ship with the treasure before the ghosts of the pirate crew return to seek their revenge.
